div.p:
In Purſuance of this Part of the Doctrine, I have a fair Opportunity given me to enter upon


the Conſideration and Reſolution of two Queſtions; 
                     viz.

3 Very groſs and abſurd are the Errors which Papiſts have framed againſt this Doctrine, who (albeit the holy Scripture doth not acknowlege any other Place than Heaven and Hell for Souls, departed from their Bodies) yet have deviſed other four beſides theſe two; 
                     viz.
                   Limbus Patrum, Limbus Infantum, a moſt pleaſant Meadow, and Purgatory.
